58">Bibliothèque apostolique vaticane</a></span></li><li><span class="nowrap uid noarchive"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://nla.gov.au/anbd.aut-an35416737">Bibliothèque nationale d’Australie</a></span></li><li><span class="nowrap uid noarchive"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.worldcat.org/identities/lccn-n79-138880">WorldCat</a></span></li></ul></div></li>
